data.description: Enjoy one level living in a home that features a master bedroom with master en suite bathroom. That is not all; it has a larger than life garage that provides adequate space for your cars and toys. The garage has a shop as well. Sit out on the deck to grill and relax. Don't forget the three season patio; at nearly 300 sq ft you can utilize this area as you see fit. This charming home is quite a value. Call me today for your personal tour of this charming home.
